title: 100. Bamboozled! Ft. Bobby Sausalito
itunes:title: 100. Bamboozled! Ft. Bobby Sausalito
description: You have been bamboozled! On today's episode, Andy and the crew are joined by comedian and internet personality, Bobby Sausalito as they discuss Coca-Cola's diversity training, the power of indoctrination and what we as Americans want this country to represent.
